Key Match Events: Jaker Ali and Anamul Haque collided while attempting to catch Pramod Madushan off Taskin Ahmed's bowling
Miscellaneous Highlights: Soumya Sarkar left the game due to a neck injury after striking the advertising board while stopping the ball
Mustafizur Rahman left the game on a stretcher due to cramping
Tanzid Hasan replaced Sarkar as a substitute fielder due to concussion protocols
Umpire Tanvir Ahmed took over for Richard Kettleborough due to heat
Others: The match was played at the Zahur Ahmed Chowdhury Stadium
